f,g : \Bbb R \longrightarrow \Bbb R
f
g
u(x,t)=f(x-at)+g(x+at)
u_{tt} = a^2 u_{xx}
\phi(x,t) = f(x-at)
\phi_{tt}(x,t) = a^2 f_{xx}(x-at)
\phi_{xx}(x,t) = f_{xx}(x,t)
\phi_{tt} = a^2 \phi_{xx}
\phi
\eta(x,t) = g(x+at)
\eta_{tt}(x,t) = a^2 g_{xx}(x,t)
\eta_{xx}(x,t) = g_{xx}(x,t)
\eta_{tt} = a^2 \eta_{xx}
\eta
u =\phi+\eta
